title: Malliotakis Defends N.Y.C. House Seat, Toppling Familiar Democratic Foe
description: Max Rose loses a comeback bid in a district that is based mainly in Staten Island.
dc:creator: Michael Gold

media:content.media:credit: Jose A. Alvarado Jr. for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Representative Nicole Malliotakis defeated Max Rose, a Democrat, for the second consecutive time.
